title: Qigong Massage - Self Massage By Dr. Jwing-Ming Yang
description:
This video teaches you to massage both the physical body and the energetic body, stimulating circulation for both. Master Yang shows simple massage techniques for your entire body, and I feel this training is vital to anyone who will be putting their hands on someone else. You can learn to really feel the various tissues, circulatory systems, and Qi energy in your own body, and be much more experienced and sensitive when you massage someone.
Very clear instruction, and great introduction to the Acupressure points and channels
